<section class="grid">
    <div>
        <h2>Threat Model</h2>
        <p>
            DigiVax assumes persistent compromise of networks, endpoints,
            identity providers, and credential systems. Security is not restored
            through detection, but rendered unnecessary through protocol design.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2>Protocol Layer</h2>
        <p>
            Trust is established pre-transaction. No session, packet, or
            instruction executes without cryptographic and structural legitimacy.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2>Operational Impact</h2>
        <p>
            Attack surfaces collapse. Cyber operations transition from
            probabilistic defense to deterministic impossibility.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

